# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:462
msgid ""
"Land cover change information, including a land cover area change matrix and"
" a spatial dataset or map that shows the areas subject to degradation, "
"improvement or no change based on land cover data."
msgstr "土地覆被变化信息，包括土地覆被面积变化矩阵和空间数据集或地图，根据土地覆被数据显示退化、改善或无变化的区域。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:464
msgid ""
"Information on land cover, land cover changes and land cover degradation "
"should be reported in km2 for the entire country."
msgstr "应以平方公里为单位报告全国的土地覆被、土地覆被变化和土地覆被退化信息。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:466
msgid ""
"If the default datasets have been replaced with national land cover data, "
"countries are encouraged to upload the relevant geospatial data to PRAIS 4. "
"Any spatial data uploaded to the system must be supported by appropriate "
"metadata describing the spatial data, as indicated in the data source form "
