# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO1.md:1456
msgid ""
"SDG indicator 15.3.1 relies on the total land area reported in table "
"CP-1.T1. Modifying that number will therefore alter the indicator’s value."
msgstr "可持续发展目标指标 15.3.1 依赖于表 CP-1.T1 中报告的土地总面积。因此，修改该数字将改变指标值。"

#: ../../SO1.md:1459
msgid ""
"The ‘Area’ fields of the spatial tables SO1-4.T3,  SO1-4.T4 and SO1-4.T5 "
